Name: 10 Minute Barbarian
About the game: 10 Minute Barbarian is a unique strategy game that combines fast-paced exploration and even faster-paced action combat. Choose your battles carefully, then watch as armies of hundreds crash castle walls, cast spells, and send fireballs into each other's ranks. Features: High-speed strategy gameplay for the busy gamer Giant battles with hundreds of soldiers supported by special units like dragons, demons, and necromancers Controls easy enough for casual players No micropayments---pay once, get everything 10 Minute Barbarian is available for Windows and Mac OS X.
